Description
-----------

Enables the player model to cast shadows.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    g_showPlayerShadow [boolean]

Parameters
----------

-   [boolean]
    -   0 - Player model does not cast shadows.
    -   1 - Player model casts shadows.

